Additionally, the paper discusses the application of these methods in the field of neuromorphic engineering, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the method's adaptability for non-stationary data streams, which is related to the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
